No bundled game data (V16; PRD Section 10.9)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Source releases of this project distribute code, schema, migrations, tests,
and parsers only. They do NOT distribute raw game-data snapshots, prebuilt
databases, artwork, audio, story scripts, voice lines, wiki/community prose,
or full announcement bodies. Users build their own local database from
approved snapshots via the `arknights-mcp import` / `arknights-mcp sync`
commands.

