  yuanyan3060 / ArknightsGameResource
    (https://github.com/yuanyan3060/ArknightsGameResource)
    Optional, off-by-default image URL REFERENCES are DERIVED at query time
    from a game_id already stored from the primary snapshot. No image bytes are
